wikipedia_page.main: Gregory Tempest (born 28 December 1993) is a Northern Irish professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Grantham Town.

response: William Grant Corkhill (23 April 1910 – 9 August 1978) was a Northern Irish footballer who played in the Football League for Cardiff City and Notts County. Corkhill's grandson Greg Tempest also became a professional footballer and played for Notts County.
